*Normalan* je život sa dvije obaveze: rad i odmor. (A normal life has two obligations: work and rest.)

Učenik je imao *normalne* ocjene na ispitu. (The student had normal grades on the exam.)

Ona je izgledala *normalno*. (She looked normal.)

Nije uobičajeno da se neko tako ponaša, to nije *normalno*. (It is not usual for someone to behave like that, it is not normal.)

Danas je *normalno* da se ljudi šalju poruke preko interneta. (Today it is normal for people to send messages over the internet.)